    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fiery jerk-spiced pork meatball curry</strong> with the <strong>garlic & lime</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop over the <strong>remaining cultured coconut </strong>and <strong>remaining jerk paste</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion </strong>and<strong> </strong>a <strong>lime</strong> <strong>wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
